Well, I be getting some, too.
But I don't make it my everything.

508
00:45:13,753 --> 00:45:15,755
Lieutenant, you still up?

509
00:45:16,798 --> 00:45:18,216
I'm here.

510
00:45:18,300 --> 00:45:20,343
