- Negative. The can is clean.

514
00:45:53,752 --> 00:45:55,795
I don't know, uncle frank.

515
00:45:55,879 --> 00:45:58,924
Putting two and two together,
and coming up with six, maybe?

516
00:45:59,007 --> 00:46:02,302
- Maybe.
- You called spiros still, right?

517
00:46:05,597 --> 00:46:07,641
Spiros will know what to do.

518
00:46:09,684 --> 00:46:13,396
Come past early tomorrow.
I wanna get down the diner first thing.

519
00:46:13,480 --> 00:46:15,190
All right.

520
00:46:19,694 --> 00:46:23,657
