539
00:48:02,088 --> 00:48:05,008
Said he didn't get married
to cook his own dinner.

540
00:48:05,717 --> 00:48:08,636
Anyway, he's cooking his own dinner now.

541
00:48:13,183 --> 00:48:16,478
What about with you and your wife?
What happened?

542
00:48:19,272 --> 00:48:20,398
She died.

543
00:48:25,195 --> 00:48:29,866
- Not now, Gus. I'm good.
- Whatever you say, Jimmy.

544
00:48:32,077 --> 00:48:35,246
- So, you about ready to go?
- Sure.

545
00:48:35,330 --> 00:48:37,832
Be right back. I just gotta make a call.

546
00:48:59,521 --> 00:49:01,856
Please enter your code now.

547
00:49:04,818 --> 00:49:08,488
- Hi, may I help you?
- Yeah, let me talk to Eve.

548
00:49:10,740 --> 00:49:13,451
