554
00:49:28,049 --> 00:49:33,972
We have a variety for you to choose from
when you arrive. When are you coming?

555
00:50:07,714 --> 00:50:10,466
Uh... just give me a minute.

556
00:50:19,434 --> 00:50:23,479
Hi. Choose a game.

557
00:50:23,563 --> 00:50:25,565
Can you guess this word?

558
00:50:35,074 --> 00:50:37,076
Hi. Choose a game.

559
00:50:38,620 --> 00:50:40,455
Can you guess this word?

560
00:50:48,046 --> 00:50:51,216
Stop! Move away from the cookie jar.

561
00:50:58,473 --> 00:51:00,475
Hi. Choose a game.

562
00:51:02,518 --> 00:51:04,687
Can you guess this word?

563
00:51:15,156 --> 00:51:17,158
Hi. Choose a game.

564
00:51:19,285 --> 00:51:21,287
Can you guess this word?

565
00:51:33,216 --> 00:51:34,676
Long day.

566
00:51:35,635 --> 00:51:37,637
Yeah, me, too.

567
00:51:51,150 --> 00:51:53,695
Thanks for the beer.

568
00:51:53,778 --> 00:51:55,780
