Hey, y'all, they coming.

570
00:52:15,425 --> 00:52:19,470
What these motherfuckers
think they looking at?

571
00:52:19,595 --> 00:52:22,098
Nigger, you done lost
your motherfuckin' mind.

572
00:52:22,181 --> 00:52:25,601
- You standing on my real estate.
- Mine now.

573
00:52:25,685 --> 00:52:29,647
- Took it while you was resting.
- Y'all too late.

574
00:52:33,735 --> 00:52:38,156
Look, I'm gonna let you walk off,
or we could do it the other way.

575
00:52:38,239 --> 00:52:41,200
Who you got to do it the other way? Them?

576
00:52:46,289 --> 00:52:49,417
- You gonna see me in your sleep.
- Yeah, I know. I know.

577
00:52:53,713 --> 00:52:56,257
That's right. Keep walking, bitch.

578
00:52:57,175 --> 00:52:59,594
They gonna come back.

579
00:52:59,677 --> 00:53:03,264
Yeah. The way we just punked them,
they got to.

580
00:53:11,189 --> 00:53:14,442
- Where is he?
- You can talk to me, frank.

581
00:53:14,525 --> 00:53:17,195
- This is bigger than you.
- I'll tell him.

582
00:53:17,278 --> 00:53:19,364
Bullshit. Come on, Nick.

583
00:53:27,955 --> 00:53:31,626
That's the Greek? That old guy?
I seen him in here before.

584
00:53:33,669 --> 00:53:35,296
Have a seat.

585
00:53:52,355 --> 00:53:55,441
A long time since we talk, eh, frank?

586
00:53:55,525 --> 00:53:57,819
- Coffee, something?
- We're good.

587
00:54:00,363 --> 00:54:02,365
What's on your mind?

588
00:54:03,616 --> 00:54:05,743
Every goddamn thing.

589
00:54:05,827 --> 00:54:08,704
For one, I think my cell
phone's being tapped.

590
00:54:08,788 --> 00:54:12,417
