That's a fair question, Niko.

605
00:55:02,300 --> 00:55:05,761
But it has to be the same for everyone -
no work, no pay.

606
00:55:05,845 --> 00:55:10,183
Whatever's in the cans,
we still gotta check them. That's work.

607
00:55:10,266 --> 00:55:13,352
- We take gas, so do you.
- You don't understand...

608
00:55:13,436 --> 00:55:16,397
I understand. No one is in this for love.

609
00:55:18,149 --> 00:55:20,151
It ain'tjust the money.

610
00:55:20,234 --> 00:55:24,489
I got things happening right now.
Things with my union. Right now!

611
00:55:24,572 --> 00:55:29,410
Not a fucking month from now, when
the legislative session is history. Now!

612
00:55:34,957 --> 00:55:38,961
Ok. We'll pay you still.

613
00:55:39,045 --> 00:55:42,507
I'm thinking of all the business
we do in the future

614
00:55:42,590 --> 00:55:44,675
