615
00:55:46,969 --> 00:55:48,638
Thanks.

616
00:55:53,559 --> 00:55:56,270
It's a new world, frank.

617
00:55:56,354 --> 00:56:00,691
You should go out and spend some
money on something you can touch -

618
00:56:00,775 --> 00:56:03,110
a new car, a new coat.

619
00:56:04,070 --> 00:56:07,073
It's why we get up in the morning, huh?

